[normal]targets will not be achieved at lowest cost 
[normal]with the current support 
[normal]programme.
[normal] Government policies to date have concentrated on adding costs to energy 
[normal]in an attempt 
[normal]to drive low carbon innovation
[normal].
[normal] However, the cumulative burden of this cost, coupled with the absence of Government incentives and funding support for 
[normal]innovati
[normal]on in 
[normal]UK manufactur
[normal]ing
[normal], is making the UK 
[normal]less
[normal] attractive
[normal] for investment
[normal].
